<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Intelligence (INT) is the stat affecting failure rate for this skill. <h3 id="head-eb337792e52ce3138e70c75c7004394a06ef027b">Divination Spells</h3>
<p>
The divination school of magic contains spells where magic is used to  psychically gain information about things. 
</p>
<p>
There are six spells available for the divination school: 
</p>

    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
<strong>Sense Monsters</strong> (school level 1) Detects all monsters near you. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 30 it allows you to sense monster minds for a while. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Sense Hidden</strong> (school level 5) Detects the traps in a certain radius around you. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 15 it allows you to sense invisible for a while. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Identify</strong> (school level 8) Asks for an object and identifies it. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 17 it identifies all objects in the inventory. 
</p>
</li>
                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 27 it identifies all objects in the inventory and in a radius on the floor, as well as probing monsters in that radius. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Reveal Ways</strong> (school level 9) Detects the doors/stairs/ways in a certain radius around you. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
<strong>Vision</strong> (school level 15) Detects the layout of the surrounding area. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At spell level 25 it maps and lights the whole level. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Greater Identify</strong> (school level 35) Asks for an object and fully identifies it, providing the full list of powers (*ID*). Cast at yourself it will reveal your powers (Self Knowledge) 
</p>
</li>

    </ol>


<h4 id="head-906abc02ff3d872f162af0a481dce9a5c5462baa">God given ability</h4>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fIntroduction_20to_20the_20Gods_20of_20ToME#head-830bd605821ee79b05019df0d67000cd17c87ff6"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Eru Illuvatar</a> at 2/3 prayer level. 
</p>
</li>
</ul>

